column8: I see no reason not to make it so.
If that is your desire, we shall call it done.
Very well, O Son of Hades.
I had suspected you would choose the same.
Go forth, then, Son of Hades.
Not worth the risk I see?
No choice is still a choice.
Do what you think is best.
If you are to extend to me an offering as this, then I believe it necessary to respond in kind. You are unerringly an interesting one, O Son of Hades.
I give my thanks to you.
A small token of my appreciation.
I wish for you to have this.
I suppose that this was unavoidable.
That was not what I had in mind.
Be careful with me, Son of Hades.
You forget yourself within my presence.
I do not care for such behavior there.
Best not to test me in this fashion.
You ought not test the limits of my kindness.
You are exhibiting a lack of judgment.
I wish to be alone, so leave me be.
I do not wish to be disturbed right now.
Do not outstay your welcome, Son of Hades.
You are quite different, Son of Hades.
That was enjoyable I have to say.
I recommend making a brief detour.
This was one of the potential outcomes of my gift.
All of this was in accordance with the Fates' design; or perhaps not.
I expected you would perish soon; but I knew not exactly how.
Your demises are unfortunate and yet a source of some amusement.
